<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <title>添加商品 - 亚马逊</title>
        <link rel="shortcut icon" href="img/favicon.ico">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=Edge,chrome=1">
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/base.css" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/add_product.css" />
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="mainBlockWidth">
            <div class="caption_box clear_both">
                <div class="fl">
                    <h1 class="size-extra-large spacing-top-large">添加商品</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="fr">
                    <div class="div-gpt-ad">
                        <a href="###" class="ad">
                            <div class="mainImg"></div>
                        </a>
                        <div class="sellercentral">Advertisement</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tutorialDefault"></div>
            <div class="grid clear_both">
                <div class="leftBlockWidth fl">
                    <div class="ReleaseNew">
                        <div class="product-heading">
                            <span class='size-extra-large'>发布一件新商品</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="color-secondary">首先搜索亚马逊商品目录</p>
                        <div id="search">
                            <div class="searchInputWidth">
                                <i class='a-icon icon-search'></i>
                                <input type="text" id="product-search" placeholder="商品名称、UPC、EAN、ISBN 或 ASIN"/>
                            </div>
                            <div class="product-search-button">
                                <button class="button button-search">搜索</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="add-a-product-group a-spacing-top-small">
                            <span>若亚马逊的商品目录中没有该商品：</span>
                            <a href="###">创建新商品信息</a>
                        </h4>
                        <h4 class="add-a-product-group a-spacing-top-small">
                            <span>要管理您的销售应用程序， </span>
                            <a href="###">单击此处</a>
                        </h4>
                        <h4 class="add-a-product-group a-spacing-top-small">
                            <span>如果您已申请GTIN豁免，</span>
                            <a href="###">请在此处检查状态</a>
                        </h4>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="rightBlockWidth fr">
                    <div class="ReleaseNew">
                        <div class="a-spacing-bottom-small">
                            <span class='a-size-large'>库存</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="draft">
                            <a href="###" class="widget-action-item">
                                商品信息草稿
                                <span class='fr Draft_listings_count'>-</span>
                            </a>
                            <a href="###" class="Suppressed_errors">
                                禁止显示
                                <span class='fr error_listings_count'>1</span>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-center">
                            <a href="###">管理库存</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>